%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as EPMS User
    participant UI as EPMS UI
    participant BFF as EPMS BFF/API Layer
    participant EPMS as EPMS Domain Service
    participant EIS as EPMP <br/>Integration Service
    participant Vault as Secrets Manager / KMS
    participant ZAuth as Zendesk <br/>OAuth/API Token Auth
    participant ZD as Zendesk API
    participant WH as Zendesk Webhook
    participant MB as Message Broker
    participant DB as EPMP DB
    participant Audit as Audit / Sync Log

    Note over EIS,Vault: One-time integration setup
    EIS->>Vault: Store OAuth client <br/>/ API token / webhook secret
    EIS->>Audit: Record connection setup

    Note over User,ZD: Ticket <br/>creation from EPMP to Zendesk
    User->>UI: Raise support<br/> issue / escalation
    UI->>BFF: Submit support request
    BFF->>EPMS: Create <br/>EPMP support case
    EPMS->>EIS: Create <br/>Support ticket
    EIS->>Vault: Fetch OAuth <br/>token / API token
    EIS->>ZAuth: Obtain / <br/>validate access token
    ZAuth-->>EIS: Access token <br/>/ auth success
    EIS->>ZD: POST /tickets <br/>with mapped EPMP fields
    ZD-->>EIS: Zendesk ticket id / status / url
    EIS->>DB: Insert EPMP case ticket 
    EIS->>Audit: Log outbound ticket creation
    EIS-->>EPMS: Ticket created successfully    
    EPMS-->>BFF: Success response
    BFF-->>UI: Show linked Zendesk ticket reference

    Note over ZD,EPMS: Near-real-time inbound update via webhook
    ZD->>WH: Ticket updated <br/>/commented / status changed
    WH->>EIS: Deliver webhook payload
    EIS->>EIS: Validate webhook signature / source
    EIS->>MB: Publish canonical support event
    MB->>EPMS: Consume support update event
    EPMS->>DB: Update support snapshot / status projection
    EPMS->>Audit: Log inbound update processing

   